Release Info:

Killer Is Dead is the latest title from the demented mind of celebrated
game creator, SUDA51, serving as a spiritual successor to his previous
cult favorites, No More Heroes and Killer 7. Stylish cell-shaded visuals
set the mood in this gritty, bloody, ultra-violent world where
biomechanical augmentations increase the power of criminals and
"executioners" alike.
